media:group.media:title: Black Widow Is A MESS
media:group.media:description:
Umm...this is different so I really hope that you guys will enjoy it.

I really enjoy making Star Wars videos but I enjoy making videos even more. And considering the fact that there isn't much new Star Wars material right now I want to explore other franchises too. I am a huge Marvel fan and was considering making an MCU project for a long time.
